'''AbioCor'''是一款[[人工心臟|全人工心臟]]（Total Artificial Heart, TAH），由总部位于[[美國|美國]][[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]的{{link-en|AbioMed|AbioMed}}公司研發。這種人工心臟可以完全植入患者体内，優點包含原件小、使用[[生物传感器|生物传感器]]等。 AbioCor的運作主要靠[[鋰離子電池|鋰離子電池]]維持其運作<ref>{{ cite journal | author = 狄特利（Steve Ditlea） | title = 人工心臟前景可期？（The Trials of an Artificial Heart） | journal = [[科學人|科學人]]中文版 | volume = 7 | date = 2002年9月 | pages = | issn = 1682-2811 }} [http://sa.ylib.com/MagArticle.aspx?Unit=newscan&id=110 內容節錄] {{Wayback|url=http://sa.ylib.com/MagArticle.aspx?Unit=newscan&id=110 |date=20170313042525 }}</ref>，由[[经表皮能量传输系统|经表皮能量传输系统]]（Transcutaneous Energy Transmission, TET）進行充电，因此AbioCor不需經由电线或管線穿透皮肤，從而减少感染的风险<ref name="HN_NMP188">{{cite web |url=https://www.healthnet.com/static/general/unprotected/pdfs/national/policies/TotalArtificialHeart.pdf |format=PDF |title=National Medical Policy - NMP188 |publisher=HealthNet |pages=17 |date=September 2015 |accessdate=15 March 2016 |archive-date=2016-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315231032/https://www.healthnet.com/static/general/unprotected/pdfs/national/policies/TotalArtificialHeart.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Regence52">{{cite web |url=http://blue.regence.com/trgmedpol/surgery/sur52.pdf |format=PDF |title=Medical Policy Manual - Policy No: 52 |publisher=Regence |pages=22 |date=December 2015 |accessdate=15 March 2016 |archive-date=2016-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319044011/http://blue.regence.com/trgmedpol/surgery/sur52.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="THIAbioCor">{{cite web |url=http://www.texasheart.org/Research/Devices/abiocor.cfm |title=Heart Assist Devices - AbioCor Implantable |publisher=Texas Heart Institute |accessdate=15 March 2016 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307073407/http://www.texasheart.org/research/devices/abiocor.cfm |archivedate=2016年3月7日 |df= }}</ref><ref name="AMAbioCorArch07">{{cite web |url=http://www.abiomed.com/products/product_details.cfm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070521005214/http://www.abiomed.com/products/product_details.cfm |title=Product Details |publisher=AbioMed |date=2007 |archivedate=2007-05-21 |accessdate=15 March 2016 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="DowlingCurrent01">{{cite journal |title=Current status of the AbioCor implantable replacement heart |journal=The Annals of Thoracic Surgery |author =Dowling, R.D. |author2 =Etoch, S.W. |author3 =Stevens, K.A. |author4 =Johnson, A.C. |author5 =Gray Jr., L.A. |volume=71 |issue=3 |pages=S147–S149 |year=2001 |doi=10.1016/S0003-4975(00)02615-1 |pmid=11265850}}</ref>。

這種人工心臟重量約一公斤，體積和一顆[[葡萄柚|葡萄柚]]相當，這樣的尺寸對於人體而言會占掉相當大的空間，因此通常只適合體型較大的男性使用<ref name = AbioCor>{{cite news | url = http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20060907/2872440/ | author = 蔡筱雯 | work = [[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] | title = 美准體內人工心臟移植 | date = 2006-09-07 | accessdate = 2017-03-12 | archive-date = 2017-03-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170313044451/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20060907/2872440/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。AbioCor的預期壽命為18個月。

